nnoremap Y y$

" Include wrapped lines when using the movement keys
set whichwrap+=<,>,h,l,[,]
nnoremap <silent> k gk
nnoremap <silent> j gj
nnoremap <silent> 0 g0
nnoremap <silent> ^ g^
nnoremap <silent> $ g$

